reviews.text: You don't usually expect good service in Hong Kong, but this little wine bar will make you feel so well cared for. The prices are great too!
lots of wine/drinks to choose and good price. Chicken wings are so tasty
Lovely little wine bar. Friendly service and bottles of good wine at good prices. Food was fun. Gets busy, so arrive early on Fridays and Saturdays.
Very good vibes. Lots of wine selections to choose from, and the staff are knowledgeable about the wines. The food is good too. I've visited this venue every time I've come back to HK.
Excellent wine choices, great staff, Matt and Steven.
